read_pepdo(
  site = c("01304562", "01304200"),
  nms = NULL,
  startDate = "2013-01-01",
  endDate = "2020-12-31"
)

Arguments

site

chr string of site numbers for USGS stations
nms

optional chr string vector of names to reassign to site numbers
startDate

chr string of start date in YYYY-MM-DD
endDate

chr string of end date in YYYY-MM-DD

data.frame

Details

Raw data are downloaded using the USGS dataRetrieval R package, this function is a simple wrapper to the readNWISuv function

Note that download the station data with the default argument may take a few minutes. 01304562 is Peconic River, 01304200 is Orient Harbor.
